snippet: Since Christina McHale won a first-set tiebreaker against her idol Serena Williams at Wimbledon last month, she's played three tournaments and World Team Tennis to prepare for the U.S. Open....
lead_paragraph: Since Christina McHale won a first-set tiebreaker against her idol Serena Williams at Wimbledon last month, she's played three tournaments and World Team Tennis to prepare for the U.S. Open.

headline.print_headline: After a Set Off Serena, McHale Aims for US Open Success
headline.main: After a Set Off Serena, McHale Aims for US Open Success
